{"tid":2334242,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"疑不滿女友出軌拳打腳踢　男警否認控罪　辯方：呢件事冇發生過","createTime":"2020-12-21T05:02:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T12:35:33.000Z","uid":56115,"like":24,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"572b99715d4ea3032858380ed7bfc2b92fae90e7","tid":2334242,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T05:02:23.000Z","msg":"28 歲男警疑不滿同為警察的女友「一腳踏兩船」，到女方寓所「攤牌」，要求查看其電話訊息不果，對她拳打腳踢。男警今（21 日）在觀塘裁判法院否認一項普通襲擊罪，案件押至 3 月 24 日開審，控方將傳召 4 名證人包括女事主，辯方不爭議閉路片段及事主醫療報告，惟稱「呢件事冇發生過」。主任裁判官徐綺薇聞言謂：「即係（爭議）誣告，唔係意外觸碰？」辯方同意。裁判官將案件訂在明年 3 月 24 日開審，被告以原有條件保釋。<br />\n<br />\n男被告女事主均為警隊衝鋒隊員"},{"pid":"41c8e8e9c01dbac1af2a7266453a93733d429c0a","tid":2334242,"uid":56115,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T05:02:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E7%96%91%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%A5%B3%E5%8F%8B%E5%87%BA%E8%BB%8C%E6%8B%B3%E6%89%93%E8%85%B3%E8%B8%A2-%E7%94%B7%E8%AD%A6%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E6%8E%A7%E7%BD%AA-%E8%BE%AF%E6%96%B9-%E5%91%A2%E4%BB%B6%E4%BA%8B%E5%86%87%E7%99%BC%E7%94%9F%E9%81%8E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E7%2596%2591%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%258F%258B%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25BB%258C%25E6%258B%25B3%25E6%2589%2593%25E8%2585%25B3%25E8%25B8%25A2-%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E6%258E%25A7%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E6%2596%25B9-%25E5%2591%25A2%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E4%25BA%258B%25E5%2586%2587%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%2594%259F%25E9%2581%258E%2F&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzAUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=d41bb11e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E7%2596%2591%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%258F%258B%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25BB%258C%25E6%258B%25B3%25E6%2589%2593%25E8%2585%25B3%25E8%25B8%25A2-%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2590%25A